g", "id": "1054410368970058", "uri": "https://scontent-fra3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38984449_1054410378970057_4740113338631946680_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=n73THFmk6pwQ7kNvgGrcOem&_nc_ht=scontent-fra3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAWkZLobCBe8-w-1A0LiJUzpdJiaU-IScFjjN__Jn7psA&oe=67028058"}, {"file_name": "Screen 4.png", "id": "931032731767339", "uri": "https://scontent-fra3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39036657_931032735100672_9161034576042090411_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=XM2qkE7JnJ8Q7kNvgGMKhvy&_nc_ht=scontent-fra3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCALBnJWDFIc1XiigxrVg-pjlg5eFDp7MFeF76zH0AtUw&oe=67028C68"}, {"file_name": "Screen 3.png", "id": "948122593026803", "uri": "https://scontent-fra3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75540503_948122596360136_5938909964869160168_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=zCxSWHF1uiEQ7kNvgGtHZLN&_nc_ht=scontent-fra3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAjIUP3z31CqMxGXsviEG9ijS7-Qvb-MxgrcSy8Wqv6Ag&oe=67028798"}, {"file_name": "Screen 5.png", "id": "3686251014977875", "uri": "https://scontent-fra3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75303838_3686251018311208_126730168301810876_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=6KVfhoXFOR0Q7kNvgEMpX-J&_nc_ht=scontent-fra3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYANuWLZxkaA8JkGEyVGKuHwLLgH1bSoAr0rGlQ9Dfuyqw&oe=67028560"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Landscape.png", "id": "424359086634465", "uri": "https://scontent-fra5-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75371506_424359089967798_6539732024548584706_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=YfLcVKcDxOoQ7kNvgFTj_tN&_nc_ht=scontent-fra5-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYANT12ggwtHXpRbi0jSqo0YKyko0HKm0-te_yLYqGFEYg&oe=67028579"}, "display_name": "Artshell Immersive Art Space", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Set up your virtual art space with Artshell on Meta Quest and Meta Quest Pro. Step out of the white cube, and finally get the immersive experience of showcasing your artworks in a new way using VR, by selecting, easily, from the archive of your Artshell account.\nWith the new Immersive Art Space experience, you can design and share art like never before. Empower your visitors to move freely, alone or with others in multi-user mode, in a large visionary space, exploring entire floors in a borderless horizon. Immersive Art Space features information on the display you have curated even with captions for individual works. Easily upload images from your Artshell account with the VR configurator to create and modify your display with Immersive Art Space on Meta Quest.\nWith Immersive Art Space artists and curators have a new tool to increase their visibility. Exhibition venues can reach a wider global audience and select the works they have always wanted to exhibit, without logistical limitations. \nVisitors can immerse themselves in this new art space from the comfort of home or anywhere else, without architectural barriers and reducing the environmental impact of their artistic passion. Immersive Art Space is a project supported by the European Union - Next Generation EU.", "short_description": "Experience the virtual exhibition space designed by Artshell. Arrange the artworks in your database in an immersive environment, to be explored in complete freedom, alone or in multi-user mode. Step out of the white cube and make your artworks viewable in a visionary space. Populate the walls of your art world with works, in high definition, accompanied by captions. Enter additional information to the display in the available in-depth supports to create a complete exhibition experience."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.artshell.eu/en/privacy-app.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Store", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.artshell.eu/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"},